name: Dog Boss
public_notice:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract - which allows contract owners to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token. The smart-contract owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.

description.en:
"DOGBOSS An BEP20 meme token that fosters and promotes healthy and widespread usage and decentralization of the project through a specific reward linked to users transactions involving decentralized wallets. At the same time, 2% of the total amount is burned from each transaction, which makes the project deflationary
"
